<div id="banner">
	<h1>Scott McCloud is Back!</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
<p><a href="http://scottmccloud.com/">Scott McCloud</a> is one of my favorite writers and his medium, comic books, simply adds to the joy of his work.</p>

<p>He’s released his new comic, <a href="http://scottmccloud.com/comics/trn/intro.html">The Right Number</a>, under a new micropayment system, <a href="https://www.bitpass.com/">BitPass</a>. (The comic costs a quarter.) I haven’t read the comic but from what I’ve heard, it’s going to be good. </p>

<p>Even better, his comicblog (a website with a new comic every day), <a href="http://scottmccloud.com/comics/mi/mi.html">Morning Improv</a> is coming back soon. This is going to be fun.</p>

<p class="posted">posted July 03, 2003 02:12 PM (<a class="category" href="cat_web_memes">Web Memes</a>)  <a href="000993" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
</div>

